Description: The initial street light Linked Data imported to the [FarolApp](http://farolapp.linkeddata.es/) application. It contains data about street lights in ten cities from four countries. Cite as:Mihindukulasooriya- Nandana- Esteban Gonzalez- Fernando Serena- Carlos Badenes- and Oscar Corcho. "FarolApp: Live Linked Data on Light Pollution." Demo at 15th International Semantic Web Conference (ISWC 2016).
